enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve modifying the state of the bag by adding or removing elements from a collection.
Both methods involve removing elements from the bag, though removeAll removes all occurrences of each element in the collection.
After calling removeAll, the bag should no longer contain any of the elements from the input collection, which can be verified using containsAll.
Both methods involve modifying the bag based on the contents of a collection, though retainAll retains elements instead of removing them.
